      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 17 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 17 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：官有渝，貞吉。出門交有功。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows us one changing the object of his pursuit; but if he be firm and correct, there will he good fortune. Going beyond (his own) gate to find associates, he will achieve merit.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
