      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 17 六三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 17 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三：系丈夫，失小子。隨有求得，利居貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows us one who cleaves to the man of age and experience, and lets go. the little boy. Such following will get what it seeks; but it will be advantageous to adhere to what is firm and correct.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
