      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 17 九四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 17 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：隨有獲，貞凶。有孚在道，以明，何咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows us one followed and obtaining (adherents). Though he be firm and correct, there will be evil. If he be sincere (however) in his course, and make that evident, into what error will he fall?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
