      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 17 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五：孚于嘉，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows us (the ruler) sincere in (fostering all) that is excellent. There will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
