      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 17 上六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上六：拘系之，乃從維之。王用亨于西山。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The topmost SIX, divided, shows us (that sincerity) firmly held and clung to, yea, and bound fast. (We see) the king with it presenting his offerings on the western mountain.</seg>
      </tuv>
